{"data":{"page":{"id":"8788ae7d-af6a-5b2c-b9d9-e10875b84500","html":"<p>As part of my work as a senior interactive developer at SapientNitro, I started to architect and build an internal application to manage the technical skills of Sapient developers across the world.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/40247/2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.099999999999994%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/dc919c74efc4afdc56fab92d9853f263/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>I got two other developers on board (for a couple of weeks) and we started to work on it. The app was built using Sails.js, an MVC framework based on Express/Node.js that creates a REST API with the endpoints defined by the models. We also connected to the Active Directory to fetch employee data and used Sapient’s user credentials to sign-up and sign-in users.</p>\n<p>The DB was driven by Mongo (we used Mongolabs for testing) and for the UI we used Bootstrap. The app allows admins to create/edit/delete new skils and categories.</p>\n<p>Developers can update their skills (using a level criteria) and managers can review them and also assign a value to them.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/40247/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 44.7%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/42f7de26f64c707648239ed2218fe6d6/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/40247/3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 49.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/6b333/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/f3ce7/3.jpg 200w,\n/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/72342/3.jpg 400w,\n/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/6b333/3.jpg 800w,\n/static/a69a349aecabcefbba608205366e5f03/40247/3.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/13fa55878eae6cc6791d3ef9f4b4c338/40247/4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/13fa55878eae6cc6791d3ef9f4b4c338/6b333/4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/13fa55878eae6cc6791d3ef9f4b4c338/f3ce7/4.jpg 200w,\n/static/13fa55878eae6cc6791d3ef9f4b4c338/72342/4.jpg 400w,\n/static/13fa55878eae6cc6791d3ef9f4b4c338/6b333/4.jpg 800w,\n/stati